  <description><![CDATA[<p>We are pleased to introduce Hotel Austria to our programme, which has recently undergone extensive refurbishments and now features a new reception and lobby area, a new dining room with house bar and a cosy cellar bar, which is a popular meeting place. The hotel is well known for its excellent food and friendly service. Situated in between Saalbach and Hinterglemm, the ski bus stops outside the hotel and intermediate skiers can ski back to the hotel at the end of the day, weather permitting.</p>]]></description>
